translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,109,Allah Taalaa hi kay liye hai jo kuch aasmanon aur zamin mein hai aur Allah Taalaa hi ki taraf tamam kaam lotaye jatay hain
  3,110,Tum behtareen ummat ho jo logon kay liye peda ki gaee ho kay tum nek baaton ka hukum kertay ho aur buri baaton say roktay ho aur Allah Taalaa per eman rakhtay ho agar ehal-e-kitab bhi eman latay to unn kay liye behtar hota unn mein eman walay bhi hain lekin aksar to fasiq hain
  3,111,Yeh tumhen sataney kay siwa aur ziyada kuch zarar nahi phoncha saktay agar laraee kay moqa aajaye to peeth mor len gay phir madad na kiye jayen gay
  3,112,Inn per her jagah zillat ki maar pari illa yeh kay Allah Taalaa ki ya logon ki panah mein hon yeh ghazab-e-elahee kay mustahiq hogaye aur inn per faqeeri daal di gaee yeh iss liye kay yeh log Allah Taalaa ki aayaton say kufur kertay thay aur bey waja anbiya ko qatal kiya kertay thay yeh badla hai inn ki na farmaniyon aur ziyadtiyon ka
  3,113,Yeh saray kay saray yaksan nahi bulkay inn ehal-e-kitab mein aik jamat (haq per) qaeem rehney wali bhi hai jo raaton kay waqt bhi kalam ullah ki tilawat kertay hain aur sajday bhi kertay hain
  3,114,Yeh Allah Taalaa per aur qayamat kay din per eman bhi rakhtay hain bhalaiyon ka hukum kertay hain aur buraiyon say roktay hain aur bhalaee kay kaamon mein jaldi kertay hain. Yeh nek bakht logon mein say hain
  3,115,Yeh jo kuch bhi bhalaiyan keren unn ki na qadri na ki jaye gi aur Allah Taalaa perhezgaron ko khoob janta hai